01438  * 1000Base-X modes.
01439  * Note: MODE bit
01440  * When MODE=1,  1000Base-X mode is selected. Auto negotiation will follow IEEE 802.3 clause 37.
01441  * When MODE=0,  SGMII mode is selected and the following note will apply.
